s/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe9052e17d46ee9b25133ffee6911b03226fb9eb","tid":469402,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T09:45:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>皇室堡有間食肆啲豆腐臭嘅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/174514_8b177940b8634e1abd3c39b3c759cc84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F174514_8b177940b8634e1abd3c39b3c759cc84.jpg&h=6013b014&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"17eed7639ed7272cc60ffab8a4cf3f3f5f1a5ccb","tid":469402,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T09:45:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>燒唔死 因為一定上唔到3000度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講緊3000celsius<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇記錯對白係3萬度,假設佢上到3萬度上唔上到個熔點<br />\n又或者導熱煮熟入面隻金鎗人又得唔得呢,唔知佢套甲入面有冇散熱配備<br />\n甚至燒到佢冇氧氣呼吸死又有冇得諗<br />\n<br />\n得閒去一轉大家食J問下金鎗人套甲有咩功能先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/174552_e0ec0daffff176875c64ad17e6afea19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F174552_e0ec0daffff176875c64ad17e6afea19.jpg&h=0aa1b52c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"987777095ba4e23dea58a05b60f7b2eec3e14b70","tid":469402,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T09:47:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>皇室堡有間食肆啲豆腐臭嘅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/174514_8b177940b8634e1abd3c39b3c759cc84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%